					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3850000#post-3903969</guid>
				<title>Re: I can&#039;t even...</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3850000/scp-3995#post-3903969</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 08 Aug 2018 21:39:27 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Captain Kirby</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3440103</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The appeal is similar to how people who like a certain book or a certain song may want to find other books or songs by the same author/band. And if you are a casual reader who does not know how wikidot works, there’s no simple way to figure out who wrote an article. So instead, they have this collapsible that shows other works in a more easily accessible manner.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
