					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm gonna use like 15&#160;MB of my data this month to tell you: this is the weirdest SCP I've ever read. And we're talking about SCPs here, so&#8230;<br /> I still can't really explain this to myself.<br /> Anyway&#8230; I also have a question. No offense, but who gives a flying <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">fu</span>&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;. frick what other stuff you wrote? Again, it's just that I've never seen anything like this before. This wasn't meant to sound like a harassment or something. It's the first time I've seen this.</p> 
